Interface TickReceiver

public interface TickReceiver

Classes that do implement this Interface will be able to register themselves to the TickGenerator.

Author:
Ciobanu Alexander

Method Summary
 void RegisteredForTicks()
          Method will be invoked when the object implementing this interface has been registered for tick notification.
 void TickReceived()
          Method will be invoked when TickGenerator has created another tick.
 void UnregisteredFromTicks()
          Method will be invoked when implementing class has been unregistered from the tick generator.
